Script ns-gen.py is for generating non-stationary mixtures of gaussians.
The output of this script uses Weka's arff dataset format 
(http://www.cs.waikato.ac.nz/ml/weka/). Run 'ns-gen --help' for details.

Script ns-plot is for plotting the generated data. Run 'ns-plot --help'
for details.

These Python3 scripts require the installation of the following modules:

1) numpy (http://www.numpy.org/);
2) scipy (http://scipy.org/);
3) matplotlib (http://matplotlib.org/);
4) liac-arff (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/liac-arff).

Enjoy!